casebody.data:
Klaus BOETTCHER, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
FEDERAL NATIONAL MORTGAGE ASSOCIATION, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1507 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 09, 2017 SUAREZ, LOGUE and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Upon consideration of appellee's motion to dismiss and appellant's response thereto, it is ordered that the above styled appeal is hereby dismissed for lack of jurisdiction.
